This paper deals with discourse analysis and natural language processing, which are both subfields of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also involves machine learning techniques for classification (cs.AI) and self-training (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper deals with annotation tasks and data analysis, which are relevant to subfields such as data science (cs.DS) and computational social science (cs.CC).
